'''短刺伊神蟹'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Izanami curtispina'''''}}），是[[短尾下目|短尾下目]]（[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]）[[饅頭蟹總科|饅頭蟹總科]][[黎明蟹科|黎明蟹科]][[伊神蟹屬|伊神蟹屬]]<ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal = [[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year = 2009 |volume = Suppl. 21 |pages = 1–109 |title = A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |author1 = Sammy De Grave |author2 = N. Dean Pentcheff |author3 = Shane T. Ahyong |display-authors=etal |url = http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |language = en |access-date = 2014-05-27 |archive-date = 2011-06-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=WoRMS_440349>{{cite WoRMS |author=P. Davie |title=''Izanami curtispina'' (Sakai, 1961) |id=440349 |year=2009 |accessdate=2013-03-21 }}</ref>的一個物種。

生活於[[東中國海|東中國海]]及[[南中國海|南中國海]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://base.sp2000.cn/colchina_c13/show_species_details.php?name_code=c9db407a-efbd-45f2-b00b-6eafd33dd4a9 |title=短刺伊神蟹  Izanami curtispina (T. Sakai,1961) |work=[[中国生物物种名录|中国生物物种名录]] |edition=2011版 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |language=zh-hans |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527220858/http://base.sp2000.cn/colchina_c13/show_species_details.php?name_code=c9db407a-efbd-45f2-b00b-6eafd33dd4a9 |archivedate=2014-05-27 }}</ref>，見於[[台灣|台灣]][[宜蘭縣|宜蘭]][[頭城鎮|頭城]]，亦偶於[[高雄市|高雄]]及[[臺南市|臺南]]發現<ref name=taibif>{{cite web |url=http://taibif.org.tw/zh/catalogue_of_life/page/7270-561b-658e-c7d8-ec64-3284-cd35-9416 |title=Izanami 伊神蟹屬 |work=[[台灣生物多樣性資訊入口網|台灣生物多樣性資訊入口網]] |accessdate=2014-05-26 |language=zh-hant |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527212541/http://taibif.org.tw/zh/catalogue_of_life/page/7270-561b-658e-c7d8-ec64-3284-cd35-9416 |archive-date=2014-05-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

